ed="T" n="0786a10"/><persName key="A010684">釋存壽</persName>，不知何許人也<ptr target="#n263"/>。清標勝範，造次奚<lb
ed="T" n="0786a11"/>及<ptr type="glossary" target="#g56"/>。罷尋經論，勇冠輩流。往問律於<persName key="A010581">石霜<roleName>禪<lb
ed="T" n="0786a12"/>師</roleName></persName>，決了前疑。虛舟<ptr type="glossary" target="#g57"/>不繫，乃為枯木眾<ptr target="#n1711"/>之椔<lb
ed="T" n="0786a13"/>杌<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1593"/>矣。後還<placeName key="PL000000005199">蒲坂</placeName>，緇素歸心。時<persName key="A010685"><name><anchor xml:id="beg0786sgsz1"/>冀<anchor xml:id="end0786sgsz1"/>王</name>友謙</persName>受<lb
ed="T" n="0786a14"/>封<ptr target="#n1710"/>屏翰<ptr type="glossary" target="#g58"/>，好奇侚異，聞人一善，厚<anchor xml:id="beg0786sgsz2"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0786sgsz2"/>下之。<ref type="person" target="#A010685">王</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0786a15"/>召入府齋，論道談玄，不覺膝之前席，頗<lb
ed="T" n="0786a16"/>增奉仰，續為菩薩戒師，供施<anchor xml:id="beg0786001"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>更</sic><corr>便</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0786001"/>蕃<ptr type="glossary" target="#g42"/>。<anchor xml:id="beg0786002"/>度<anchor xml:id="end0786002"/>門<lb
ed="T" n="0786a17"/>人四百許員，尼眾百數。<persName key="A010684">壽</persName><anchor xml:id="beg0786sgsz3"/>平<anchor xml:id="end0786sgsz3"/>日罕言，言必利<lb
ed="T" n="0786a18"/>物。喜慍之色，人未嘗見，望之若孤松凌雪<lb
ed="T" n="0786a19"/>焉。終時春秋九十三，加趺而坐，一月後髭髮<lb
ed="T" n="0786a20"/>再生，重剃入塔。塔之亭，每有虎旋遶，𠫗跡<lb
ed="T" n="0786a21"/>時繁。勅諡為<persName key="A010684">真寂大師</persName>焉<ptr target="#n1712"/>。</p>
